---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
const links = [
  { label: 'Claude Code',     href: '/categoria/claude-code' },
  { label: 'Claude',          href: '/categoria/claude' },
  { label: 'Novas IAs',       href: '/categoria/novas-ias' },
  { label: 'Atualizações',    href: '/categoria/atualizacoes' },
  { label: 'MCPs',            href: '/categoria/mcps' },
  { label: 'Skills & Agents', href: '/categoria/agents' },
];
---

<footer class="mt-20 border-t border-slate-800 bg-slate-900">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 py-12">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-10 sm:grid-cols-3">
      <!-- Marca -->
      <div class="col-span-1">
        <a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <img src="/logo.svg" alt="AIgora" class="h-7 w-auto" />
        </a>
        <p class="mt-3 text-sm text-slate-500 leading-relaxed max-w-xs">
          O melhor da inteligência artificial em português — Claude Code, MCPs, Agents, novas IAs e muito mais.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Categorias -->
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-400 mb-4">Categorias</h3>
        <ul class="space-y-2">
          {links.map(({ label, href }) => (
            <li>
              <a href={href} class="text-sm text-slate-500 hover:text-slate-300 transition-colors">{label}</a>
            </li>
          ))}
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- Newsletter -->
      <div>
        <h3 class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-400 mb-4">Newsletter</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-4">
          Receba o compilado das principais notícias a cada quinzena.
        </p>
        <a href="/newsletter" class="inline-flex rounded-lg bg-brand-gradient px-4 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity">
          Inscrever-se grátis
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-10 border-t border-slate-800 pt-6 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-3">
      <p class="text-xs text-slate-600">© {year} AIgora. Todos os direitos reservados.</p>
      <p class="text-xs text-slate-600">Feito com <span class="text-indigo-500">♥</span> em pt-BR</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
